                  <h3 class="font-semibold">Required Reason API Detection</h3>
                  <span class="text-[10px] font-bold bg-accent/20 text-accent px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded uppercase">New</span>
                </div>
                <p class="text-sm text-muted mb-2">Scans your Swift source for Required Reason API usage (UserDefaults, file timestamps, disk space, boot time, etc.) and verifies matching privacy manifest declarations. The <strong class="text-white">#1 privacy-related rejection reason</strong> in 2024.</p>
