                <div><span class="text-muted">$</span> <span class="text-accent-light">shiplint scan ./MyApp.xcodeproj</span></div>
                <div><span class="text-muted">$</span> <span class="text-accent-light">shiplint scan .</span> <span class="text-muted text-xs ml-2"># also works with Package.swift â€” no .xcodeproj needed</span></div>
